Name: Blueprints™
About the game: Blueprints is a 3D third-person parkour platformer game where the more levels you beat, the prettier they get. Run, walk, jump, and fall through this mediocre game that I am begging you to buy. Experience beautiful natural (and not natural) landscapes in this short casual adventure you are very likely to forget. Play all sorts of parkour challenges (and a random 2 minutes of holding [W]) in this 3-hour adventure of a lifetime. It's not quite an adventure of a lifetime, but still a good adventure.
